metadata.name: CryptoOx #1 - Happy Moo Year!
metadata.description:
[CryptoOx #1 -- Click to see its detail in 3D](https://cryptoox.co/ox/1)
Gong hei fat choy! The Genesis Collection celebrates the lunar new year, with our first eight oxen. Which one will bring you the most luck? Chúc mừng năm mới!

The crackle and boom of firecrackers all around, the scent of gunpowder and incense in the air. Music and lights and red and gold surround you. Welcome to the Year of the Ox.
